        <h3>BioPerine (Piperine)</h3>
        <p>Black pepper extract that inhibits glucuronidation enzymes in the liver and intestine. Increases curcumin absorption by up to 2000%. The most common and cost-effective absorption enhancer in supplement formulations.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="info-card">
        <div class="info-card-ico"><Icon name="droplet" size={22} /></div>
        <h3>Water-Soluble Technology</h3>
        <p>Micelle or nano-emulsion delivery systems that make lipophilic curcumin water-dispersible. Absorption increases of 40-185x over standard curcumin. Used in premium brands like Qunol and NovaSOL formulations.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="info-card">
        <div class="info-card-ico"><Icon name="shield" size={22} /></div>
        <h3>Phytosome Delivery</h3>
        <p>Curcumin bound to phosphatidylcholine (lecithin) to create a lipid-compatible complex. Meriva phytosome technology shows 29x better absorption than standard curcumin. Excellent tissue distribution and retention.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="info-card">
        <div class="info-card-ico"><Icon name="target" size={22} /></div>
